<title>UK: Merrill Lynch ups FRN to 300 bln lire.</title>
<headline>Merrill Lynch ups FRN to 300 bln lire.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-02-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following floating-rate issue, announced earier by joint lead managers Credito Italiano and Merrill Lynch, has been increased to 300 billion lire from 200 billion lire.</p>
<p> BORROWER   MERRILL LYNCH AND CO INC</p>
<p> AMT    300 BLN ITL   BASE	 3M-LIBOR  MATURITY    05.MAR.99</p>
<p> TYPE	 FRN	 MARGIN     +5 BP     PAY DATE    05.MAR.97</p>
<p> LAST MOODY AA3	 ISS PRICE  PAR	 FULL FEES   10 BP</p>
<p> LAST S&amp;P   AA-	 REOFFER    PAR</p>
<p> LISTING    LONDON    DENOMS (M) 5-50	SALE LIMITS US/UK/IT</p>
<p> NEG PLG    YES	 CRS DEFLT  NO	  FORCE MAJ   NO</p>
<p> GOV LAW    N.Y	 HOME CTRY  U.S	 TAX PROVS   STD</p>
<p> MGT/UND    5 BP	SELL CONC  5 BP	PRAECIPUUM  =</p>
<p> NOTES	ISSUED OFF MTN PROGRAMME</p>
<p>-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 8863</p>
